{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/returning-boolean-values-from-functions","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Vracanje Boolean Vrednosti iz Funkcija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mozda se secate iz lekcije <a href=\"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-equality-operator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Poredjenje sa operatorom jednakosti</a> da svi operatori poredjenja vracaju boolean vrednosti <code>true</code> ili <code>false</code>.</p>\n<p>Ponekad ljudi koriste <code>if/else</code> iskaz da obave poredjenje, ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function isEqual(a, b) {\n  if (a === b) {\n    return true;\n  } else {\n    return false;\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ali postoji bolji nacin. Posto <code>===</code> vec vraca <code>true</code> ili <code>false</code>, mozemo direktno vratiti rezultat poredjenja:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function isEqual(a, b) {\n  return a === b;\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"5679ceb97cbaa8c51670a16b","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite funkciju <code>isLess</code> tako da uklonite <code>if/else</code> iskaz.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18273,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/returning-boolean-values-from-functions"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function isLess(a, b) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n  if (a < b) {\n    return true;\n  } else {\n    return false;\n  }\n  // Only change code above this line\n}\n\nisLess(10, 15);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>isLess(10, 15)</code> treba da vrati <code>true</code></p>","testString":"assert(isLess(10, 15) === true);"},{"text":"<p><code>isLess(15, 10)</code> treba da vrati <code>false</code></p>","testString":"assert(isLess(15, 10) === false);"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da koristite nijedan <code>if</code> niti <code>else</code> iskaz</p>","testString":"assert(!/if|else/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"returning-boolean-values-from-functions","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-early-pattern-for-functions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/replacing-if-else-chains-with-switch","id":"5679ceb97cbaa8c51670a16b","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/returning-boolean-values-from-functions"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}